response.overview: Even before there was video, there was Swedish Erotica. With millions of volumes sold worldwide for over twenty years, Swedish Erotica is the most successful film and video series of all time. Now re-edited and re-mastered into four solid hours of the raunchiest classic erotica ever produced. Re-Digitized Footage featuring Eva Allen in scenes from: A Perfect Night; Cheers to Us; The Dressmaker; Paradise Lost; Screams & Moans; Only Teach Me; The Secret.
response.title: Swedish Erotica 126
